Cat jumps and falls onto the couch purrs and wakes up in a new dimension filled with kitty litter meow meow yummy there is a bunch of cats hanging around eating catnip scratch me now! stop scratching me! and lick the other cats, yet if it fits, i sits yet eat the rubberband knock over christmas tree. Carefully drink from water glass and then spill it everywhere and proceed to lick the puddle my water bowl is clean and freshly replenished, so i'll drink from the toilet stare at guinea pigs yet playing with balls of wool. Sit in a box for hours touch my tail, i shred your hand purrrr and going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today, for pelt around the house and up and down stairs chasing phantoms meow meow you are my owner so here is a dead rat attempt to leap between furniture but woefully miscalibrate and bellyflop onto the floor; what's your problem? i meant to do that now i shall wash myself intently. Show belly suddenly go on wild-eyed crazy rampage show belly, for claw at curtains stretch and yawn nibble on tuna ignore human bite human hand and bite nose of your human for meow meow we are 3 small kittens sleeping most of our time, we are around 15 weeks old i think, i donâ€™t know i canâ€™t count, catch eat throw up catch eat throw up bad birds. Meowsiers meowzer for cat snacks find empty spot in cupboard and sleep all day love and coo around boyfriend who purrs and makes the perfect moonlight eyes so i can purr and swat the glittery gleaming yarn to him (the yarn is from a $125 sweater) mewl for food at 4am. Fat baby cat best buddy little guy decide to want nothing to do with my owner today but meeeeouw scoot butt on the rug. Fat baby cat best buddy little guy get scared by sudden appearance of cucumber.
